snippet.title: One Last GoB (feat. James Holt) (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
(Streaming and Download links below!)
The war is nearing its end...

This is the official music video for the song "One Last GoB (feat. James Holt)" from the GoB 2020 original game soundtrack. It is a personal tribute to the 4 years of development the game went through, calling back to iconic weapons and characters that have developed both fame and infamy over the games lifetime. 

It was written by Sayincraft Studio's: Scott Warren (aka me), and performed by the very talented James Holt. James Holts's vocals and instrumental truly exceeded all expectations, and I can't recommend checking out his other works enough! (I'll link them below.)

Special shoutout to Ethan (Kaiser), and Sarah (Emo Goose) for helping me film the extra character movements in the video.

***

James Holt: https://www.youtube.com/user/jamesholtartist
https://www.jamesholtmusic.com/

***

Subscribe, like, and follow me on other social media for more updates on GoB, and future games from Sayincraft Studios!

GoB Official Discord: https://discord.gg/S3St6SF

GoB 2020 Soundtrack:
Spotify: https://open.spotify.com/album/4hSxVECzYUKxg4n9to0ksi?si=UcVKJVjZS9mUATEutCgEFw
Itunes/Apple Music: https://music.apple.com/us/album/gob-2020-original-game-soundtrack-single/1531498491

***

GAME DOWNLOADS:
Itchio: https://sayincraft.itch.io/gob-2020
GameJolt: https://gamejolt.com/games/GoB2020/537471

***

GoB Release Trailer: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mZvA92N5l5I&ab_channel=SayincraftStudios

***

Social Media and Stuff:
Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/sayincraft
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/sayincraft/#
Twitter: https://twitter.com/Sayincraft

https://www.sayincraft.com/

Remember, not everything is as it seems...
